== Intro ==
We tested this in Chrome, FireFox and Opera, and it seems to work in all of
them, however we're more confident in Chrome for now.

== Instructions ==
Chrome on Windows (w/o webserver)

(1) Close all Chrome windows (otherwise the commandline switch won't work)
(2) Open commandline
(3) cd c:\_changeMe_\AppData\Local\Google\Chrome\Application\
(4) chrome.exe --allow-file-access-from-files
(5) open (2015)_trbl_-_ninkasi/index.html
